snippet.title: King Arthur II - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The new Fantasy RTS "King Arthur II" is now live. No longer a valiant ruler, King Arthur is now the Maimed King trying to mend a land almost beyond repair in a stunning new plot. Developed by Neocore Games, check out King Arthur II on PC.

Gather your army and head to IGN for more info:
http://pc.ign.com/objects/097/097682.html

Subscribe to IGN's channel for reviews, news, and all things gaming: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ignentertainment
